= Choose a Württemberg coalition

A coalition is selectable if it controls at least **41** of the **80** Landtag seats. If no listed coalition has a majority, the incumbent Württemberg government may continue as a minority cabinet.

- @wurttemberg_select_spd_ddp
- @wurttemberg_select_spd_ddp_dvp
- @wurttemberg_select_spd_ddp_z_dvp
- @wurttemberg_select_ddp_z_dvp
- @wurttemberg_select_ddp_z_dvp_wbwb
- @wurttemberg_select_z_dvp_wbwb_dnvp
- @wurttemberg_select_z_wbwb_dnvp
- @wurttemberg_select_z_wbwb_dnvp_csvd
- @wurttemberg_select_wbwb_dnvp_nsdap
- @new_wurttemberg_elections: Call new Württemberg Landtag elections.
- @root: Continue without changing the Württemberg government.

